<h2>How to load/import external javascript/jquery through js file.<br></h2><div><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"><br><br>In the event that you need to incorporate a JS document in a JS you can utilize jQuery for that</div><pre><code>$.getScript('another_file.js', function() {<br>    //script is loaded and executed put your dependent JS here<br>});</code></pre><div>Also, in the event that you can't utilize jQuery</div><pre><code>var imported = document.createElement('script');<br>imported.src = '/path/to/imported/script';<br>document.head.appendChild(imported);</code></pre><br><b>Are this article be help you ?.
